						<p>Hoysaḷa, Vīra Sōmēśvara, 23rd year, Tai 11, Thursday = A.D. 1258.</p>						

						<p>This records that the <hi rend="italic">mahāpradhāni</hi> Siṅgaṇṇa-deṇḍanāyakkar, who was the son of <hi rend="italic">mahāpradhāni</hi> Siṅgaradēva-daṇḍanāyaka set up the image of goddess in the temple.</p>						

